    "2904:103": "none“> kūpaghaṭikānipāte nāśabaddhapravartena ca",
    "2904:104": "toyanigandha - kīṭaṃ vā bhavet praṇāli - niḥsṛtānpravāhayet srotāmbuṃ",
    "2904:105": "nānāvidhapravartenañca svāminaṃ caturvarṣeṇa athavā pradhāna - svajanabandhuviprayogo bhaviṣyati tasya",
    "2904:106": "śāntirjalajāgapūjākūpapratiṣṭhādanaṃ kṣīrapātraṃ guḍapātraṃ ghṛtapātraṃ suvarṇagarbhaṃ",
    "2904:107": "datvā ācāryaviprāya vā vadet |",
