    "2904:116": "agnibhayavivādaḥ ca tasya śāntiḥ daśadinalaṃghitena juhuyāt yajñaṃ",
    "2904:117": "navagrahapūjāṃ ca kṛtvā dānadaśarajanikā 10 tena pratirūpaṃ kṛtvā ācāryaviprāya",
    "2904:118": "vā dadyāt rātrau baliṃ kṣatrapālāya dadyāt saṃghāya bhojyaṃ ca tena",
