    "2904:127": "none“> mārjārakalaharathavā mṛtyurbhavet mahākalaha",
    "2904:128": "athavā bhāryāśokaṃ ca raudradevatāpraveśanaṃ ṣaṇmāsāta śāntiḥ prabhāte nityaṃ",
    "2904:129": "snātvā kalaśapūjanaṃ homaṃ ca dānarūpe mayātmapratirūpaṃ kṛtvā gurave vā brāhyaṇāya",
    "2904:130": "vā dadyāt saṃghabhojyaṃ ca tena śāntiḥ |",
