    "2904:138": "none“> gṛhe sarpapraveśena svāmimṛtyurpañcavarṣaiḥ",
    "2904:139": "māsena vā athavā dhanakṣayaśatrubhayaṃ ca adhunāśanaṃ śāntisapradinābhyantare",
    "2904:140": "prayogaṃ kartavyaṃ upacārataḥ snānaṃ prabhāte karoti ,",
    "2904:141": "juhuyāt yajñavidhivat triloha - trikatu - trifalā - trimadhu - tririṣakāṣṭhena samidhaṃ saptavrihiṃ saptaśakabījaṃ ,",
    "2904:142": "kalaśadvayaṃ balitriṃśatpramāṇaṃ",
    "2904:143": "naivedyasahitaṃ svālabaliṃ ekaṃ aṇḍaṃ ekaṃ punanaivedyadvayaṃ matsyamāṃsarūdhiradhidugdhamadhunā",
    "2904:144": "sarpapraveśasthāne mṛttikāṃ gṛhītvā ucchiṣṭasthāne nikṣipet",
    "2904:145": "dānacandrabimbavidhivat kāśapātre kṣīraghṛtascāyuritaṃ hiraṇyagarbhadaśaratikā",
    "2904:146": "yathā śaktisuvarṇadakṣiṇāṃ gurave viprāya vā dadyāt saṃghabhojyaṃ ca tena śāntiḥ",
