    "2904:165": "none“> bṛha ndali mālādṛṣṭena mahāśokamahābhaya - āyāsa athavā triviyoga vināśanaṃ ca varṣatrayeṇa",
    "2904:166": "tasya śāntiyajñaṃ juhuyāt kalaśaūjanaṃ ekaṃ dāna guḍapātraṃ śaktito hiraṇyagarbha",
    "2904:167": "dattvā mahābaliṃ dadyāt saṃghabhojyaṃ ca tena śāntiḥ |",
