    "2904:173": "none;text-autospace:",
    "2904:174": "none“> snānena pādāṅge mūtrapātena mahārogabhayaṃ",
    "2904:175": "dhanakṣayaṃ viṣṭhayā putraśokaṃ viṣṭhāmedhate rogeṇa kuṭumbanāśanaṃ varṣatrayeṇa",
    "2904:176": "śāntiḥ balividhiḥ dvātriṃśat tathaiva naivedya 3 taṇḍulakūṭaṃ ekena pacyate",
    "2904:177": "tena aodanena snānarūpaṃ kṛtvā pañcopacāravidhinā pūjayet pañcāt",
    "2904:178": "dvārapālasthāne kṛtvā pañcopacāravidhinā pūjayet pañcāśatadvārapālasthāne nikṣipet",
    "2904:179": "dānarajatakośapātraṃ guḍapātraṃ ,",
    "2904:180": "suvarṇapātraṃ śaktito hiraṇyadakṣiṇāṃ dadyāt saṃghabhojyaṃ ca | |",
