    "2904:199": "akasmāt mṛtakaṃ tu prāpta dṛśyatena svāmimṛtyurvarṣa catuṣkena śāntihomaṃ",
    "2904:200": "juhuyāt dānatilapātraṃ hiraṇyagarbhaṃ kṛtvā lohapātraṃ madhupūrṇaṃ tathaiva ca",
