    "2904:211": "bhavet tasya śāntiḥ prabhāte yajñakarmapañcarakṣāpāṭhaṃ sahasrāvartanaṃ ca",
    "2904:212": "dānagobhūmihiraṇāni datvā mainākasthāne patanakāṣṭhādīnāṃ nadyāṃ pravāhayet",
    "2904:213": "sthānādhipatipūjāṃ yajñavidhinā pūjayet |",
