    "2904:233": "śāntitīrthaṃ gatvā śaktito rajatadāna pratiṣṭhāṃ bhojyaṃ udyānasthāne",
    "2904:234": "kalaśadvayasthāpya - kāṃsyapātre",
    "2904:235": "trimadhupūritaṃ suvarṇagarbhaṃ pratiṣṭhādānaṃ mahābalikriyāṃ kṛtvā gaṇacakraṃ",
